snippet.title: WonderSwan Color Longplay - Run=Dim - Return to Earth (OLD)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Mad-Matt

Fairly easy shootemup on the WonderSwan.  I couldn't begin to tell you what the story is but i suspect its a real bad guy on a space station that's terrorizing the earth and someone needs to go up there and take him out, namely you and kick his ass back down to earth. -
